---

<BaseLayout title="Contact" description="Prendre contact avec Ismail El Jamiy.">
  <div class="page-container">
    <header class="page-header">
      <div class="page-eyebrow">Me contacter</div>
      <h1 class="page-title">Contact</h1>
      <div class="page-rule-short" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    </header>
    <p class="intro">
      Je suis heureux d'échanger avec des chercheurs, collaborateurs et toute personne
      intéressée par le patrimoine arabe, la HTR ou la vision par ordinateur. Le meilleur
      moyen de me joindre est l'e-mail.
    </p>
    <div class="links-list">
      {links.map(link => (
        <a href={link.href} target={link.href.startsWith('mailto') ? undefined : '_blank'}
           rel={link.href.startsWith('mailto') ? undefined : 'noopener noreferrer'}
           class="contact-row card">
          <span class="contact-icon" set:html={link.icon} />
          <div class="contact-text">
            <span class="contact-label">{link.label}</span>
            <span class="contact-value">{link.value}</span>
          </div>
          <svg class="contact-arrow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16"
               viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
               stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>
    <div class="location-note">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
           stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/>
        <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
      </svg>
      Toulouse, France
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-container { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 1.5rem 5rem; }
  .page-header { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .page-title { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem); font-weight: 600; color: var(--fg); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .intro { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--fg-muted); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .links-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .contact-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.25rem; padding: 1.125rem 1.25rem; text-decoration: none; color: var(--fg); }
  .contact-row:hover { transform: translateX(3px); }
  .contact-icon { color: var(--accent); flex-shrink: 0; display: flex; }
  .contact-text { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.1rem; flex: 1; }
  .contact-label { font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 0.775rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--fg-muted); }
  .contact-value { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--fg); }
  .contact-arrow { color: var(--fg-muted); opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
  .contact-row:hover .contact-arrow { opacity: 1; color: var(--accent); }
  .location-note { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--fg-muted); }
</style>
